issues.body:
Hi - I'm having issues using `mcp-obsidian` with the desktop Claude app on macOS complaining about an API key... but that hadn't been an issue in the past. Let me know if I'm missing something. 

macOS version: 15.5
npm version: 11.3.0
Claude Desktop version: 0.10.14 (27cc6f)

logs from Claude app
```
2025-06-11T17:17:18.961Z [mcp-obsidian] [info] Initializing server... { metadata: undefined }
2025-06-11T17:17:19.002Z [mcp-obsidian] [info] Server started and connected successfully { metadata: undefined }
